{"ja337:0.1":"Jataka ","ja337:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja337:0.3":"Kokilavagga ","ja337:0.4":"7. Pithajataka ","ja337:1.1":"“Na te pithamadayimha, ","ja337:1.2":"na panam napi bhojanam; ","ja337:1.3":"Brahmacari khamassu me, ","ja337:1.4":"etam passami accayam”. ","ja337:2.1":"“Nevabhisajjami na capi kuppe, ","ja337:2.2":"Na capi me appiyamasi kinci; ","ja337:2.3":"Athopi me asi manovitakko, ","ja337:2.4":"Etadiso nuna kulassa dhammo”. ","ja337:3.1":"“Esasmakam kule dhammo, ","ja337:3.2":"pitupitamaho sada; ","ja337:3.3":"Asanam udakam pajjam, ","ja337:3.4":"sabbetam nipadamase. ","ja337:4.1":"Esasmakam kule dhammo, ","ja337:4.2":"pitupitamaho sada; ","ja337:4.3":"Sakkaccam upatitthama, ","ja337:4.4":"uttamam viya natakan”ti. ","ja337:5.1":"Pithajatakam sattamam. "}